Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:35.74,DefaultBG,,0,0,0,,{\fs46\pos(730,590)\an4\fr8\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}也找優他們來\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:35.74,DefaultBG,,0,0,0,,{\fs46\pos(750,710)\an4\fr8\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}當然還有春輝❤\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,下禮拜的煙火大會 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,當然還有春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟春輝同學看煙火...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻說要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻真是的 說什麽沒在跟春輝交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽看他們都是互相喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓他們約會 在一起才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在正在念書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 看煙火當然也有加優一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡那種人擠人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我找別人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,決定了 就跟那個人開心的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過好像很好玩 其實也是挺想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,既然決定了就得準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}念書加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿姨 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法專心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,會太緊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝同學會說什麽呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他會覺得我可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等盂蘭盆節過完 就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去跟救美櫻的那個人打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對方有聯絡過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,說是應該可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,應該可以什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有忘記東西吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,該出門了吧 拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我就説甚平裝穿起來舒服比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}剛才在家裡也...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麽你們兩個會一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛在那碰個正著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's Go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能見到那位恩人了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 盂蘭盆節之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎樣的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,超期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為什小夏會期待呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因為因為 不是很浪漫嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對方見到美櫻一定也會非常開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,當然會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟妳保證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不可以亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來 啊 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻喜歡這種的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,優他們?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有已讀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 我們兩個自己逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,氣氛很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣快點交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小燈好可愛 真的是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 要不要跟她說話呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 做不到做不到做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在太沒骨氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走了啦 夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那兩個人自己去吧 順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不是肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我請妳吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要...烤香腸 烤魷魚 奶油馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還有巧克力香蕉 冰糖葫蘆 棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是想讓我破產嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快點來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不等你們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻 妳還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有點熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我買冷飲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 煙火都開始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我也想休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,恩人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,妳剛才不是在跟夏樹說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前受一個人幫助過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很想跟他道謝 但都沒有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,現在終於能見到那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人是男生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玉屋~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs56}原本是放煙火的商行, 因爲曾經與另一家煙火商競演, 民衆會在煙火升空時喊煙火商的名號來支持雙方, 演變成現今看煙火的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 玉屋是什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不知道還喊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡看不到耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝同學 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡休息就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,難得都來看煙火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 自己看也沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,畫畫還順利嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我還在猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...我很期待妳的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻不是說過沒辦法面對鏡頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽說呢 這是電影社最後一部電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是集大成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話 我希望美櫻也能參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,戀愛的顏色 大概不止一種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管不順利時 會變得像黑色夜幕一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要一點點轉變 心情就會無比高昂 產生許多色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世界就變得萬般絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就好比煙火一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,10公分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,若是能比10公分更加靠近...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我去買些吃的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,戀愛是煙火的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺能畫出戀愛的畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,救了我的那個人是怎樣的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,會不顧危險 捨身去救位素未谋面的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是誰都辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好感謝他才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫我拿著花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,救了美櫻的那個人啊 就長眠在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像本來身體就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊 美櫻不需要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對方父母也這麽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,介意是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,芹澤...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了帶火柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去剛那家店買一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明智老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,合田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老師怎麽會來這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來替朋友掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,芹澤千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:58.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「ねぇこっちおいでよ...なんて」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:05.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「えーっと、聞こえてますよ...なんて」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:05.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(801,970)}き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}1,2,3,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「もう冬ですね」「そうクリスマス」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(642,970)}ふゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1278,970)}くりすます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:15.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「どこか行きたい?」「部屋でもいいよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:15.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(654,970)}い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:15.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1107,970)}へや
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「みんな呼ぼうか?」「二人きりがいいのに...」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(559,970)}よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1011,970)}ふたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:23.57,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「冗談だよ、そのつもり」「もー!」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:23.57,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(562,970)}じょうだん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「予約したんだ」「わーオシャレなお店!」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(467,970)}よやく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1167,970)}おしゃれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1453,970)}みせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「...落ち着かないな」「無理しちゃったね」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(483,970)}お
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(610,970)}つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1087,970)}むり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「何頼もうか?」「メニューが読めないです(汗)」
