Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(399,970)}たの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(915,970)}めにゅー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1138,970)}よ
